        "text": "So I am actually starting with Featured App rewards first.\n\nOur thinking is that we can migrate to the decentralized credentials later, but we don't want to launch without app rewards. I realize the former is closely tied to us onboarding to the utility so the token will be transferable, so I will have to figure it out anyway soon.\n\nSo as I see, I need to create FeaturedAppActivityMarkers, since our actions are not CC transfers: <https:\/\/github.com\/hyperledger-labs\/splice\/blob\/1e592174d377ef4908c0847ea5b6ccb53739a67d\/daml\/splice-amulet\/daml\/Splice\/Amulet.daml#L254>\nI am looking to add it to Account (DA and WA) creation, and every mint\/burn action. We also need to have <https:\/\/docs.sync.global\/app_dev\/api\/splice-amulet\/Splice-Amulet.html#type-splice-amulet-featuredappright-765|FeaturedAppRight>, on Devnet I can assign this to myself (my party? So this again won't work for decentralized party that simply I take it)\n\nFor minting rewards, the repo you sent I can't access, but im guessing this is the same: <https:\/\/github.com\/hyperledger-labs\/splice\/blob\/2100cb1c1154c6232ab6fc0886d7c7fdeaa4e30a\/daml\/splice-amulet\/daml\/Splice\/AmuletRules.daml#L113>\n\nAnd iirc the decentralized party will need some automation to exercise a governance choice, to actually mint the rewards\n\nI wonder if there is an example out there, where this flow comes together I could use (other projects already using this, maybe open source? :crossed_fingers:), or even a doc, or its figuring it out from source?\nThe closest useful I found are these scripts:\n <https:\/\/github.com\/digital-asset\/cn-quickstart\/tree\/main\/quickstart\/daml\/external-test-sources\/splice-amulet-test\/daml\/Splice\/Scripts>,\n and this I guess: <https:\/\/github.com\/digital-asset\/cn-quickstart\/blob\/main\/quickstart\/daml\/external-test-sources\/splice-token-standard-test\/daml\/Splice\/Testing\/Registries\/AmuletRegistry.daml|https:\/\/github.com\/digital-asset\/c